title: Amulet 1-6 by Kazu Kibuishi (Scholastic)
description:
Amulet is a graphic novel series by Kazu Kibuishi published by Scholastic.

Emily along with her mother, Karen and younger brother, Navin move to their great-grandfather's house after their father dies in a car accident. The locals believe that the house is haunted, but Karen ignores the rumors. Before long, a sinister creature lures the kids' mom through a door in the basement. Desperate not to lose her Emily and Navin follow her into an underground world inhabited by demons, robots, and talking animals
